 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span><br><br>The final end was like a punch in the gut. It made me sit back and think about everything that happened in the book and if the ending any different would have been more satisfying. Not sure, maybe this is the best way it could have ended...</["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></["br"]></span>
